OL,3,CHundreds of jobs lost as Welsh
OL,4,Cfurniture manufacturer collapses
OL,6,FNearly 300 workers have been made
OL,7,Fredundant after a Flintshire-based
OL,8,Ffurniture manufacturer fell into
OL,9,Fadministration.
OL,11,FWestbridge Furniture Limited, based in
OL,12,FHolywell, first appointed
OL,13,Fadministrators from Interpath in
OL,14,FMarch. However it has now been
OL,15,Fconfirmed 297 jobs have been made
OL,16,Fredundant.
OL,18,FThe company cited "operational
OL,19,Fdisruption, weak trading and the loss
OL,20,Fof a key customer" as contributing to
OL,21,Fthe decision.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
