OL,3,CHundreds of jobs lost as Welsh
OL,4,Cfurniture manufacturer collapses
OL,6,FAccording to its website, Westbridge
OL,7,Fmanufactured furniture for brands such
OL,8,Fas Next, John Lewis and Sofology.
OL,10,FIn a statement, Chris Pole, Managing
OL,11,FDirector at Interpath and joint
OL,12,Fadministrator of Westbridge Furniture
OL,13,FLimited, said: "The team at Westbridge
OL,14,Fhas shown exceptional professionalism
OL,15,Fin maintaining production while we
OL,16,Fexplored options.
OL,26,@uD@POU
