PN,46203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F462A1776957067
OL,3,CHundreds of jobs lost as Welsh
OL,4,Cfurniture manufacturer collapses
OL,6,F"Regrettably, as no viable offers for
OL,7,Fthe business were received, it was no
OL,8,Flonger possible to continue trading
OL,9,Fand we have had to take the difficult
OL,10,Fdecision to close the business. We
OL,11,Frecognise this has been a challenging
OL,12,Fperiod for staff, and I'd like to
OL,13,Fexpress my sincere thanks for their
OL,14,Fcommitment."
OL,16,FAdministrators said production ceased
OL,17,Fon 2 April with operations maintaining
OL,18,Fafter this time as the wind-up process
OL,19,Fcontinued.
