OL,3,CHundreds of jobs lost as Welsh
OL,4,Cfurniture manufacturer collapses
OL,6,FThey said the sale of the exclusive
OL,7,Fintellectual property and design
OL,8,Frights to the full Westbridge
OL,9,Findependent product catalogue to sofa
OL,10,Fand upholstery manufacturer,
OL,11,FWhitemeadow have been agreed.
OL,13,FThey say they intend to engage with
OL,14,Fstockists of Westbridge products to
OL,15,Fensure continuity where possible.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
