OL,3,CHundreds of jobs lost as Welsh
OL,4,Cfurniture manufacturer collapses
OL,6,FChris Pole added: "The agreement to
OL,7,Fsell the IP and design rights to
OL,8,FWhitemeadow preserves Westbridge's
OL,9,Frange for retailers. We wish the
OL,10,FWhitemeadow team all the best as it
OL,11,Fembarks on a development programme to
OL,12,Freintroduce those designs to the
OL,13,Fmarket."
